if (record.value > record.previous.value) {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.GREEN
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
} else {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.PINK
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
}

panelDataJavascriptCode.name: New Panel Data Javascript Code
panelDataJavascriptCode.code:
if (record.prediction > 0) {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.APPLE_GREEN
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
} else if (record.prediction < 0) {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.PINK
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
} else {
    textColor = UI_COLOR.DARK
    valueColor = UI_COLOR.GREY
    textSize = 16
    valueFontSize = 16
    textOpacity = "1"
    valueOpacity = "1"
}
